1. Establish a sheriff may establish additional requirements for approval of
electronic bonds in a parish.
2. Require electronic bond providers maintain a registry of approved electronic
bond agents in each parish.
3. Establish procedures for the use of electronic bonds.
4. Allow the payment of bonds by automated clearing house (ACH).
5. Provide effective date.
6. Make technical changes.
